item.description:
Hi Seacoast Theater lovers come participe in a great show as we check out "The Dueling Pianos" where the audience participates in the show with the dueling piano players acting as ringmasters. Audience members send up their requests, sing-a-long or even get up on stage to dance to the music. Piano players pit one-side-against-the -other...country versus rock or men versus women...while everyone bellows out lyrics to familiar songs. Dueling Pianos, featuring the Honky Catz, takes unexpected turns and is one-of-a-kind entertainment that maximizes fun and laughter for all.

We will be having dinner at 6pm at the "Governors Inn" before the Show.

Other meetup groups will be attending!

Doors open at 7 pm,

Tickets $16 / 18

We will meet in the lobby at 7:30.

See you there!

Peter
